N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4230.14 - Intimidation, collusion

State Regulations

Any person who shall attempt to prevent another person
from claiming any horse in a claiming race, or any owners running in claiming
races who may make any agreement for the claiming of each other's horses may be
punished by the judges or they may refer the matter to the commission for
further action. Notes
